  "2026-03-07T14:45:41.111Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence: pm test pm-bdz5 --run passed (8/8); pm test-all --status in_progress passed (1 linked test); pm test-all --status closed passed (items=129 linked_tests=341 passed=62 failed=0 skipped=279); node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage reports 100% statements/branches/functions/lines."
